channel.title: Tome - Cmon (Experimental Dark RNB)
channel.description:
Hey ! I'd like to share my new song, "Cmon", it has a lot of influences from many genres, every part of the song varies a lot. its my most diverse work to date and its all made on auxy. please listen to it and lemme know what yall think :slight_smile: you can listen to it [here](https://soundcloud.com/melodiesbytome/cmon) i also have a lyric visualizer for it on youtube [here](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2XqvqYu4cxM&t=2s)
i hope you all enjoy it !

item.title: Tome - Cmon (Experimental Dark RNB)
item.dc:creator: blakkaz
item.description:
I had a listen to this yesterday and really enjoyed it!
Anything labelled ‘experimental dark rnb’ instantly gets my attention.

My initial impressions after first listen were that it could do with just a little more polish, but there’s definitely a gem underneath.

item.title: Tome - Cmon (Experimental Dark RNB)
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
Really nice continuing to hear tracks with lyrics around here, I like this. Some of the instrumentation is maybe a little out of place. Like around 2:30 there’s springy sounding synth it’s not jiving with me much. But that’s just preference really.

Otherwise, it’s slick I enjoyed it I saw you posted this a couple days ago and was like “I gotta get on this” but it’s tough on the weekends. Glad I stole ten mins to take a quick peek
